<h3>Our Review Process</h3>
Our reviews are based on extensive research and, when possible, hands-on testing. Each time you make a purchase through one of our independently-chosen links, we’ll receive a percentage of the proceeds. Read more about how we’re supported <a href="https://allaboutcats.com/affiliate-disclosure" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">here.</a>
</div>
<p>With a name like “World’s Best,” you should have high expectations for this brand. Unlike other brands that use inexpensive, low-quality materials, all of this brand’s products are made with natural compressed corn for a lightweight, dust-free litter that allows both you and your cat to breathe easy.</p>
<p>Their multiple cat formulas offer long-lasting odor control, and every formula is flushable for easy disposal. Simply put, World’s Best sets a new standard for cat litter.</p>
