<h3>Pros:</h3>
<ul class="pro">
<li>Excellent clumping action, easy to scoop.</li>
<li>Naturally absorbent compressed corn materials absorb liquid on contact.</li>
<li>Subtle natural scent, no added fragrance.</li>
<li>Very low dust and relatively low tracking compared to clay litters.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cons:</h3>
<ul class="con">
<li>May develop a foul odor when exposed to a large amount of urine.</li>
<li>Offers moderate odor control, requires frequent scooping for better results.</li>
</ul>
<p>This litter comes in 7, 14, and 28-pound bags. Because the litter is made from compressed corn rather than clay, it is lightweight compared to most traditional cat litters.</p>
</div>
<div class="su-row card-review">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span class="product-review-heading">#2 </span><a href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:worlds-best-cat-litter-review/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fworlds-best-cat-litter-clumping%2Fdp%2F37468" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"><u>World’s Best Cat Litter Clumping Formula</u></a></h2>
<p><a href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:worlds-best-cat-litter-review/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fworlds-best-cat-litter-clumping%2Fdp%2F37468" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-18268 aligncenter" src="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Worlds-Best-Cat-Litter-Clumping-Formula.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="280" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="amz" href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:worlds-best-cat-litter-review/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fworlds-best-cat-litter-clumping%2Fdp%2F37468" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">View On Chewy</a> <a class="amz" href="https://www.amazon.com/WORLDS-LITTER-Original-Unscented-32-Pounds/dp/B087QTCXPS/?tag=wwwallabou001-20" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">View On Amazon</a></p>
<p>Made from natural compressed corn materials, this clumping cat litter is free from silica dust so you and your cat can breathe easy. It forms tight, hard clumps for easy scooping, and it is biodegradable and flushable for easy disposal. This cat litter is eco-friendly and unscented, making it an excellent choice for single cat and multi-cat households.</p>
<p>Like the other formulas tested, this litter produced a little dust when first pouring but it settled quickly and was not a long-lasting issue. The litter did take on an unpleasant odor when exposed to large volumes of urine, but frequent scooping was sufficient to control litter box odor. The litter itself had a very slight scent to it but nothing strong enough to irritate cats with sensitive noses.</p>
