<h3>Pros:</h3>
<ul class="pro">
<li>Forms hard, tight clumps on contact with urine and feces.</li>
<li>Very low dust (no silica dust) compared to clay litters.</li>
<li>Eco-friendly and all-natural, clumps are flushable for easy disposal.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cons:</h3>
<ul class="con">
<li>May take on an unpleasant odor when exposed to lots of liquids.</li>
<li>Lightweight corn kernels may track more than heavier cat litter.</li>
<li>Offers moderate odor control, needs frequent scooping for better control.</li>
</ul>
<p>This litter comes in 7, 14, and 28-pound bags. Because the litter is made from compressed corn rather than clay, it is also lightweight, just like the previous product reviewed above.</p>
</div>
<div class="su-row card-review">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span class="product-review-heading">#3 </span><a href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:worlds-best-cat-litter-review/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fworlds-best-cat-litter-lavender%2Fdp%2F37591" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"><u>World’s Best Cat Litter Lavender Scented Multiple Cat Clumping Formula</u></a></h2>
<p><a href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:worlds-best-cat-litter-review/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fworlds-best-cat-litter-lavender%2Fdp%2F37591" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-10114" src="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/World’s-Best-Cat-Litter-Lavender-Scented-Multiple-Cat-Clumping-Formula.jpg" alt="World’s Best Cat Litter Lavender Scented Multiple Cat Clumping Formula" width="800" height="450" srcset="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/World’s-Best-Cat-Litter-Lavender-Scented-Multiple-Cat-Clumping-Formula.jpg 800w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/World’s-Best-Cat-Litter-Lavender-Scented-Multiple-Cat-Clumping-Formula-600x338.jpg 600w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/World’s-Best-Cat-Litter-Lavender-Scented-Multiple-Cat-Clumping-Formula-768x432.jpg 768w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/World’s-Best-Cat-Litter-Lavender-Scented-Multiple-Cat-Clumping-Formula-624x351.jpg 624w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="amz" href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:worlds-best-cat-litter-review/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fworlds-best-cat-litter-lavender%2Fdp%2F37591" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">View On Chewy</a> <a class="amz" href="https://www.amazon.com/Multiple-Cat-Lavender-Scented-32-Pounds/dp/B087QRVP77/?tag=wwwallabou001-20" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">View On Amazon</a></p>
<p>This scented formula offers the same hard-clumping benefits as the other two formulas, with the addition of a pleasant lavender scent. Generally speaking, World’s Best Cat Litter offers average odor control – when exposed to a significant amount of urine it can retain some odor. In this case, the lavender scent helps to mask that odor, keeping the litter box smelling fresher for longer.</p>
<p>In addition to its pleasant scent, this cat litter is eco-friendly and flushable. It forms hard clumps on contact with both solid and liquid waste, relying on the benefit of the fresh lavender scent to control odors for longer than average. It is very low in dust and low-tracking as well, helping you keep your house clean. Plus, it is formulated for multiple cat households.</p>
