<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-36344">
<article id="comment-36344" class="comment">
<header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard">
<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7736f34fb37f4742b8d4beee277870ce?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7736f34fb37f4742b8d4beee277870ce?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' loading='lazy' decoding='async' /><cite><b class="fn">Dan</b> </cite><a href="https://allaboutcats.com/worlds-best-cat-litter-review#comment-36344"><time datetime="2019-12-15T11:03:59+00:00">Dec 15, 2019 at 11:03 am</time></a> </header>
<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>I have used this litter for years, and the friends I have introduced to it love it as well. We had on open box in our hallway to serve our multiple cats and were always amazed at the lack of any unpleasant odors. It&#8217;s eco-friendliness is a bonus.</p>
</section>
<div class="reply">
<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-36344' data-commentid="36344" data-postid="10110" data-belowelement="comment-36344" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Dan" aria-label='Reply to Dan'>Reply</a> <span>&darr;</span> </div>
