<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>Love this litter but what I don&#8217;t understand why this company has a lavender scented option. As LAVENDER IS TOXIC TO CATS IN ANY FORM. If this company truly cares about animals how about not using scents that are toxic to pets.</p>
</section>
